      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Vincent Tang</b>\n</p><p><b>Vincent Tang</b>,<br />\na software developer and computer chess programmer based in London. He is author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> <a href=\"/Topple\" title=\"Topple\">Topple</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>,\ndeveloped since 2016, and first published in June 2018 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2016\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2016</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2017.2F18\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2017/18</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2019\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2019</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vincent_Tang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2016\">2016</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vincent_Tang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2016\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=60495\">Improving search speed</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 15, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=60625\">Why is my engine making no progress in the endgame?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 27, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=60637\">Engine testing hardware</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 28, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60719\">PVS/NegaScout: Actual benefits</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 06, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">PVS</a>, <a href=\"/NegaScout\" title=\"NegaScout\">NegaScout</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60769\">Is there a \"correct\" mate score for Fine#70?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 10, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Lasker-Reichhelm_Position\" title=\"Lasker-Reichhelm Position\">Fine #70</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=60912\">Best way to debug search speed?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 23, 2016</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2017.2F18\">2017/18</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vincent_Tang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2017/18\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65526\">Transposition table and Fine#70</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 23, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a>, <a href=\"/Lasker-Reichhelm_Position\" title=\"Lasker-Reichhelm Position\">Fine #70</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67599\">Debugging a transposition table</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 29, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Debugging\" title=\"Debugging\">Debugging</a>, <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a>, <a href=\"/Lasker-Reichhelm_Position\" title=\"Lasker-Reichhelm Position\">Fine #70</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67685\">Topple</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 09, 2018</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2019\">2019</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vincent_Tang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2019\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69532\">Automated tuning... finally... (Topple v0.3.0)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 08, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69889\">Strange draw scores when searching Fine#70</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 12, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Lasker-Reichhelm_Position\" title=\"Lasker-Reichhelm Position\">Fine #70</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69927\">On failing high and finding mates</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 16, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-High\" title=\"Fail-High\">Fail-High</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=70074\">Testing the implementation of Syzygy</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 02, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71707\">Why does stockfish randomise draw evaluations?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 01, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a>, <a href=\"/Draw_Evaluation\" title=\"Draw Evaluation\">Draw Evaluation</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vincent_Tang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/konsolas\">konsolas (Vincent) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://keybase.io/konsolas\">konsolas (Vincent Tang) | Keybase</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vincent_Tang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/konsolas/ToppleChess\">GitHub - konsolas/ToppleChess: UCI chess engine</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67685\">Topple</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 09, 2018</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228150854\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 55/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 110/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2